---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="お問い合わせ">
	<div class="contact-intro">
		<p>広島Unity勉強会が主催するイベントへの参加申請やお問い合わせは、以下のサイトおよびSNSをご利用ください。</p>
	</div>

	<div class="contact-grid">
		<section class="contact-card">
			<div class="card-header">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i>
				<h3>イベント参加申し込み</h3>
			</div>
			<p>イベントの告知と参加申し込みは主にconnpassで行っています。<br><small>※メンバー加入いただくと定期的に当イベントのほか、広島近辺の3DCGイベントについてご案内します</small></p>
			<div class="action-area">
				<a href="https://hirouni.connpass.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn connpass">
					connpass グループを表示
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="contact-card">
			<div class="card-header">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i>
				<h3>アナウンス・SNS</h3>
			</div>
			<p>最新情報やお知らせ、活動の様子を配信しています。</p>
			<div class="sns-list">
				<a href="https://www.facebook.com/hiroshimaunity" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="sns-item facebook">
					<i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i> Facebook
				</a>
				<a href="https://x.com/HiroshimaUnity/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="sns-item x-twitter">
					<i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i> X (Twitter)
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="contact-card">
			<div class="card-header">
				<i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i>
				<h3>ユーザコミュニティ</h3>
			</div>
			<p>開発の相談や雑談など、ヒロユニDiscordサーバで。</p>
			<div class="action-area">
				<a href="https://discord.gg/RkfvMRq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn discord">
					Discordに参加する
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<div class="contact-note">
		<p>※個別のご相談や詳細なご質問は、イベント会場や上記SNS、Discordにてお気軽にお声がけください。</p>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.contact-intro {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: left;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #555;
	}

	.contact-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.contact-card {
		background: #fff;
		border: 1px solid #eee;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
	}

	.contact-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
	}

	.card-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card-header i {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--secondary);
		background: #fff1f6;
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 10px;
	}

	.card-header h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.contact-card p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		flex-grow: 1;
		color: #666;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.action-area {
		margin-top: auto;
	}

	.btn {
		display: block;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: filter 0.2s;
	}

	.btn.connpass {
		background-color: #d31d00;
		color: white;
	}

	.btn.discord {
		background-color: #5865F2;
		color: white;
	}

	.btn:hover {
		filter: brightness(1.1);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.sns-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.8rem;
	}

	.sns-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.8rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		padding: 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: bold;
		border: 1px solid #eee;
		transition: background-color 0.2s;
	}

	.sns-item.facebook {
		color: #1877F2;
	}

	.sns-item.x-twitter {
		color: #000;
	}

	.sns-item:hover {
		background-color: #f8f9fa;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.contact-note {
		background-color: #f8f9fa;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
		color: #777;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.contact-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
